Package: repo-tools-remove
Architecture: any
Depends:
Description: A universal dependency for anything installed to create a repo.
        This serves as a universal dependency for anything installed
        to support creating, running, maintaining, a repo.
        A removal of this file will remove everything added by the
        installation of the repo package.
